=== Ubuntu ===

1. Install build dependecies
	sudo apt-get install build-essential libqtgstreamer-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev libdcmtk2-dev libwrap0-dev libssl-dev

2. Make Makefile:
	qmake CONFIG+=dicom beryllium.pro

3. Make Beryllium:
	make

=== Suse ===

1. Install build dependecies

        sudo zypper addrepo http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/multimedia:/libs/openSUSE_12.3/ opensuse-multimedia-libs
        sudo zypper addrepo -f -n packman http://packman.inode.at/suse/openSUSE_12.3 packman

        sudo zypper install make qt-devel qt-gstreamer-devel libQtGlib-devel dcmtk-devel tcp_wrappers-devel openssl-devel

2. Make Makefile:
	qmake-qt4 CONFIG+=dicom beryllium.pro

3. Make Beryllium:
	make

